{"ID":"20260305082131-ix3prpq","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ix3prpq","title":"优化版演讲稿(改)","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-ccmb0s9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ccmb0s9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"舌尖上的华科，时代中的我们——从食堂到外卖的饮食变迁"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-y2cvhu9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-y2cvhu9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"开场白（3分钟）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vdf8vud","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vdf8vud","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"PPT提示：封面页 + 研究背景"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fkgmdx3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fkgmdx3","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尊敬的老师，亲爱的同学们：大家下午好！"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fq0p5pv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fq0p5pv","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"今天我们想和大家分享的，是一个关于吃饭的故事——一个我们每个人都亲身参与，却可能从未细细品味的时代故事。它的名字叫 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"《舌尖上的华科，时代中的我们——从食堂到外卖的饮食变迁》"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ujv348z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ujv348z","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：封面）"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这份分享的时间轴，从1952年华中工学院建校之初，一直延伸到我们正在经历的2025年。我们尝试着去拼接和回顾的，不仅仅是菜单的变化、支付方式的升级，更是想透过\"吃饭\"这件小事，去看见背后时代的洪流，以及我们每个人在其中留下的身影。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-98il80c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-98il80c","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：研究背景与资料说明）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们翻阅了一些零星的校史记载，查询了网上资料，并结合我们自身从高中到大学，关于\"吃\"的鲜活体验，尝试勾勒出这条跨越73年的饮食变迁线。其中或许有不够精确的地方，但我们希望呈现的，是一幅有温度的时代画卷。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：引入主题图片，如一张丰盛的外卖订单与一张老饭票的对比图）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"饮食，是我们最日常的生活瞬间，却也像一面最真实的镜子，清晰映照出国家发展的轨迹和社会变迁的脉搏。从\"拿着粮票去食堂\"到\"拿着手机点外卖\"，这背后的故事，关乎便利，关乎选择，更关乎我们这代人与新时代的同频共振。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-7qw2nln","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-7qw2nln","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"接下来，就让我们一起走进时光长廊，看看华中大的\"味道\"，是如何一步步变成我们今天熟悉的模样。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-qgykolk","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qgykolk","updated":"20260305082131"}},{"ID":"20260305082131-r7lchmw","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-r7lchmw","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第一部分：供给制与大锅饭时期（5分钟）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-9sll8w1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9sll8w1","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"PPT提示：计划经济背景 + 食堂建设 + 配给制度"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-qd587tn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qd587tn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：1952年建校背景）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1952年，新中国刚刚成立三年，百废待兴。也正是在这一年，华中工学院在喻家山下诞生。建校初期的饮食制度，深深地烙着计划经济的印记，那是整个国家\"勒紧裤腰带搞建设\"的缩影。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-a6h3q4t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-a6h3q4t","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：早期饮食制度）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"根据对华中大学早期情况的记载，1950年代实行的是\"学生伙食委员会包给厨子\"的管理模式。这是一种完全的供给制：统一标准菜制，三餐固定供应。早餐是稀饭馍馍，午晚餐提供四荤，甚至还配有牛奶补品和晚间宵夜。这样的伙食标准，在当时物质普遍匮乏的大环境下，体现了国家对高等教育和人才培养的高度重视与稀缺资源的倾斜分配。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-tycsuim","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-tycsuim","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：食堂建设）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在食堂建设方面，1956年是关键年份。这一年，后来被称为\"一食堂\"的学校大食堂建成，同时教工食堂也投入使用。当时全校只有2-3个综合性食堂，服务着约900名学生。这种\"小而集中\"的规模，与今天拥有37个食堂的\"美食王国\"形成鲜明对比，却也真实反映了建国初期高校建设的务实与艰辛。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-33cwfnn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-33cwfnn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：配给方式）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"配给方式上，实行的是饭票制加定量供应。每一张粮票、每一份餐食都严格按计划分配。采购模式则是完全的政府统购统销，食材由武汉市粮食部门按人头定额划拨，不存在任何市场采购行为。这种模式源于当时国家的总体经济体制——一切为了保障基础供应，一切为了集中力量推进工业化建设。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-i4m77o7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-i4m77o7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：时代精神）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这个时期正值新中国建立初期，国家实行严格的计划经济，物资普遍短缺。高校作为国家重点人才培养基地，其饮食供应体现了\"保障基本生存\"的首要目标。\"计划食用、杜绝浪费\"不仅是食堂墙上的标语，更是那个时代的精神写照——勤俭、自律、集体优先，是一代人的真实记忆。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-trrg15v","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-trrg15v","updated":"20260305082131"}},{"ID":"20260305082131-jg92c4n","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-jg92c4n","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第二部分：文革时期的停滞与维持（3分钟）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ad637x0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ad637x0","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"PPT提示：文革背景 + 维持运转 + 物资紧缺"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-0basat3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-0basat3","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：文革背景）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文革期间，全国范围内的政治运动和社会动荡不可避免地影响了学校的正常运行，饮食服务在这一时期进入了维持基本运转的阶段。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-9lf3kda","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9lf3kda","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：配给延续）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"该阶段的资料档案较少，学校总体配给方式延续了之前的票证制度。由于全国经济波动和生产力受到影响，供应质量明显下降。历史资料中提到的\"双蒸饭\"等特殊烹饪方法，成为这个时期物资紧缺的真实写照——通过两次蒸煮使米饭体积增大，既反映了物资匮乏的现实，也展现了人们在困难时期的智慧与韧性。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-f8tweup","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-f8tweup","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：建设停滞）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在食堂建设方面，这一时期没有任何新建或改建的记录，校园餐饮设施完全依靠前期建设的食堂维持运转。这种\"只使用、不更新\"的状态，与当时全国基本建设投入大幅减少的整体情况相符。与此同时，农业生产和食品供应体系也受到冲击，进一步影响了高校的饮食保障能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-7cl59u0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-7cl59u0","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：服务韧性）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尽管面临诸多困难，学校的饮食服务仍然坚持运转，确保了师生的基本生活需求。这种在特殊时期维持基本服务的能力，体现了学校后勤系统的韧性和责任感，也为我们理解那个特殊年代提供了重要的历史视角。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-tv1e4cf","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-tv1e4cf","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第三部分：市场化转型探索期（4分钟）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-asp367t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-asp367t","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"PPT提示：改革开放 + 双轨制 + 建设恢复"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-opxulqr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-opxulqr","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：改革开放背景）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"改革开放的春风吹进校园，饮食制度开始了从纯供给制向有限市场化的历史性转变。这一时期的变化，与当时中国轰轰烈烈的经济体制改革步伐紧密相连。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-bq6qqc2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-bq6qqc2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：制度松动）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1980年代，伴随着农村家庭联产承包责任制的推广和城市经济体制改革的启动，农产品供应逐渐丰富。这一宏观背景直接体现在我们的校园餐桌上：食堂开始打破完全统一的配给模式，虽然主食仍保留计划配给制，但副食品供应已逐步放开。一个充满时代印记的细节是：当时食堂不提供公共餐具，学生们需要自备饭盒——这既反映了计划经济时期的习惯延续，也预示着个性化消费时代的萌芽。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-em6zcl2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-em6zcl2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：多样化趋势）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"到了1990年代，随着邓小平南巡讲话和社会主义市场经济体制目标的确立，食堂的饭菜选择呈现出明显的多样化趋势。学生们不仅能够吃到更具地方风味的菜肴，偶尔还能在校园里品尝到一些外来风味小吃。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-o2zsanw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-o2zsanw","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：采购变革）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"采购模式也发生了深刻变化，从过去单一的行政划拨转变为\"计划内划拨+计划外采购\"的双轨制。这意味着，部分蔬菜、肉类开始通过新兴的农贸市场等渠道进行补充。这种转变正是当时全国范围内推行的价格双轨制在高校饮食领域的具体体现——在保证基本供应的同时，逐步引入市场机制。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-jjubzor","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-jjubzor","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：建设恢复）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"食堂建设开始迎来恢复性增长。二食堂于1981年开建，教工食堂在1980年进行了首次改造。到1990年底，全校食堂数量估计不超过5-6个。这种建设步伐，不仅与文革时期的停滞形成鲜明对比，更反映了国家对高等教育投入的恢复和增加，以及高校办学规模的逐步扩大。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ewuq4e5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ewuq4e5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：时代意义）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这个过渡时期，承前启后，意义重大。它仿佛一个清晰的信号，标志着改革开放的春风已经吹遍神州大地，正从方方面面深刻改变着国家和人民的命运。从校园餐桌的悄然变化，到整个中国社会的日新月异，这场伟大变革证明了唯有解放思想、与时俱进，才能迎来民族的复兴与国家的富强，为我们今天享有的美好生活奠定了最坚实的基础。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kc3sq5t","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kc3sq5t","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第四部分：全面深化改革时期的规模化与智能化转型（2000-2012年）（4分钟）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xqzaga3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xqzaga3","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"PPT提示：合并背景 + 规模化发展 + 支付变革"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-3sjmpad","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3sjmpad","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：新世纪背景）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进入21世纪，伴随着中国正式加入世界贸易组织（WTO），改革开放进入全面深化阶段。这一重大历史决策，不仅推动中国经济以更快的速度融入全球体系，也为高校后勤服务的社会化改革注入了强大动力。2000年，原华中理工大学、同济医科大学、武汉城市建设学院合并组建新的华中科技大学，这次意义深远的高等教育资源整合，标志着我校饮食服务迈入规模化、集团化发展的新阶段。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-k2ui6hs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-k2ui6hs","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：制度创新）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在制度层面，学校积极探索并实行了保障性伙食与风味小吃并行的双轨制改革。这一创新实践与2008年教育部《高等学校学生食堂伙食结构及成本核算指导意见》的精神高度契合。更重要的是，它体现了在中国经济持续快速发展的宏观背景下，高校后勤服务在\"保障基本民生\"与\"满足多元需求\"之间寻求平衡的改革智慧。数据显示，这一时期中国GDP年均增长率保持在10%左右，国家财政性教育经费支出占GDP比例首次突破4%，为高校基础设施和服务能力的提升提供了坚实保障。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-u7rrbwx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-u7rrbwx","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：建设爆发）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"食堂建设呈现出爆发式增长。根据可查证的资料，到2012年，全校食堂数量已从世纪初的不足10个迅速增长至30余个。这种快速增长并非孤立现象，而是与中国城镇化加速推进、高等教育从精英化向大众化转变的时代背景紧密相连。具体建设项目清晰可见：四食堂于2003年建成；五食堂于2009年开建；西苑食堂在2012年完成了重要改造。这些项目的持续推进，不仅反映了学校办学规模的扩大，更是国家持续加大高等教育投入的生动体现。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-cqf31l9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cqf31l9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：支付革命）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"支付方式的变革尤为显著。2000年代中期，校园一卡通系统开始全面取代传统饭票，标志着从\"票证时代\"向\"电子支付时代\"的历史性跨越。这一转变的背后，是中国电子信息产业的快速崛起和金融基础设施的日益完善。同时，采购模式也向着更加市场化、专业化的方向演进，开始建立与大型供应商和农产品基地的\"一对一\"直采合作，供应链效率和质量控制水平得到显著提升。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-h1hrwf6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-h1hrwf6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：时代机遇）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"特别值得一提的是，这一时期中国成功举办了2008年北京奥运会等一系列国际盛事，国家综合实力的提升和国际影响力的扩大，为包括高校在内的各行各业创造了更加开放、自信的发展环境。这种时代氛围也深刻影响着校园饮食服务的理念更新和服务升级，为后续智能化、多元化发展奠定了坚实基础。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-dubmtmv","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-dubmtmv","updated":"20260305082131"}},{"ID":"20260305082131-h6p2ado","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-h6p2ado","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第五部分：新时代高质量发展与智慧服务（2012-2025年）（5分钟）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-dqrxjex","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-dqrxjex","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"PPT提示：新时代特征 + 选择丰富 + 外卖革命 + 数据支撑"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ryb7zza","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ryb7zza","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：新时代背景）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2012年党的十八大以来，中国特色社会主义进入新时代。这不仅是一个时间概念，更是我们每个人都能切身感受到的生活巨变的开始。从我们的餐桌到我们的口袋，从我们的选择到我们的体验，新时代的气息无处不在。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-o3gm890","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-o3gm890","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：选择升级）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先，我们最直观的感受是："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"选择变得前所未有的丰富"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。曾经，我们的父辈在大学时代，面对的可能是窗口有限的几个菜品；而今天的我们，在华中大的校园里，就能品尝到天南海北的风味。食堂数量从2012年的30余个发展到现在的36-38个，不仅数量增加，更重要的是品质的提升。从传统的\"四菜一汤\"到如今的小火锅、麻辣香锅、日式料理、西餐牛排，我们的味蕾体验发生了质的飞跃。更重要的是，这种丰富不仅仅体现在食堂里——2015年左右，移动支付全面接入校园，扫码点餐、线上支付成为常态，这为我们打开了另一扇大门。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5jizp3k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5jizp3k","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：外卖革命）"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"这扇大门就是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"外卖时代的到来"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这不仅仅意味着\"送餐上门\"的便利，更是一场深刻的\"时空革命\"："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-hruosyr","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hruosyr","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-aovg9tz","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-aovg9tz","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-k5qezz2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-k5qezz2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"空间上"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：我们的选择半径从校园内的几十个食堂，扩展到周边数公里的上百家餐厅。想吃川菜、日料、网红甜品，只需在APP上轻轻一点。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vas18ch","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vas18ch","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-lni7dxr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-lni7dxr","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"时间上"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：吃饭不再需要严格遵守食堂的开放时间。深夜自习后，一碗热腾腾的宵夜也能准时送达宿舍楼下。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vbj28fp","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vbj28fp","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-b3gk20s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-b3gk20s","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"方式上"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：从\"到点吃饭\"到\"随时用餐\"，从\"集体就餐\"到\"个性选择\"，我们的饮食方式发生了根本性变革。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-q64fsof","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-q64fsof","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数据显示，我校日均外卖订单量已超过万单，这充分说明了外卖已经成为我们生活中不可或缺的一部分。这种\"所想即所得\"的便利，彻底改变了我们的时间管理和生活方式。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-aiaviex","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-aiaviex","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：生活哲学）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这些变化背后，是新时代赋予我们的全新生活哲学："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"更自主、更高效、更个性化"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。我们不再被动接受有限的选择，而是主动创造适合自己的生活方式。一顿饭的选择，折射的是整个时代的发展轨迹。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-3xd3x5w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3xd3x5w","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们这一代人，正是站在互联网革命和新时代起点上的亲历者。从食堂到外卖，从饭票到刷脸支付，这些变化不仅仅是技术的进步，更是时代给予我们这代人的独特礼物。在这个过程中，我们不仅是变化的见证者，更是新时代的参与者和创造者。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-bxnwpuj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-bxnwpuj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：数据支撑）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"让我们用几个数据来感受这种变化的力量："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kbkaf18","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kbkaf18","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-16zne7v","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-16zne7v","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-quvrpx4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-quvrpx4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"中国移动支付用户规模超过10亿"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-cb66xqh","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cb66xqh","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-5p2q6b9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5p2q6b9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"外卖市场规模突破1万亿元"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-3qdxw16","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3qdxw16","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-h8bgyry","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-h8bgyry","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"网上零售额连续多年保持两位数增长"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5730ikd","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5730ikd","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-2i44htj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2i44htj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我校智慧食堂系统每日处理订单超过2万单"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xshnf2a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xshnf2a","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这些数字背后，是我们每个人日常生活的真实写照，也是新时代中国发展的生动注脚。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-qg0yo3b","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qg0yo3b","updated":"20260305082131"}},{"ID":"20260305082131-pz1mcol","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-pz1mcol","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第六部分：时代变迁与个人成长（4分钟）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-a9dfw01","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-a9dfw01","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"PPT提示：历史脉络 + 三代对比 + 多维变革 + 未来展望"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：历史回顾）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"回顾73年的发展历程，从1952年建校初期的计划配给，到今天的智能化餐饮服务，我们看到的不仅是一条饮食制度演变的脉络，更是一幅国家发展、社会进步与个人成长交相辉映的时代画卷。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xq4b5ax","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xq4b5ax","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：制度演变）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在配给制度方面，我们经历了从纯配给制到双轨制，再到票证完全废除的过程。在补贴方式上，实现了从暗补到明补的转变。在采购模式上，完成了从行政划拨到市场采购，再到基地直采的升级。这一系列变革背后，是中国从计划经济到市场经济转型的宏大叙事。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-qgxvvc1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qgxvvc1","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：三代记忆）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"作为亲历这一变迁的华科学子，我们这一代人是无比幸运的。我们的个人选择自由度，与时代发展紧密相连："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-o9k6eph","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-o9k6eph","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-hyjozp6","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hyjozp6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-ncz0hm6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ncz0hm6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们的祖辈，面对的是别无选择的计划配给，他们的故事是关于\"生存\"与\"集体\""}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-oobonu7","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-oobonu7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-d1pg22q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-d1pg22q","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们的父辈，迎来了选择有限的市场萌芽，他们的故事是关于\"改善\"与\"奋斗\""}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5oiwvos","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5oiwvos","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-teq1o21","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-teq1o21","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"而今天的我们，享受的是由互联网和AI赋能的前所未有的选择自由和个性化服务，我们的故事是关于\"品质\"、\"效率\"与\"自我实现\""}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-cyk3nfu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cyk3nfu","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：多维变革）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"新时代给我们带来了深刻的多维变革："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-rsxf3cm","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-rsxf3cm","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-jzw035x","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-jzw035x","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-3xeg2zu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3xeg2zu","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"物质的极大致富"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：不仅是菜品从\"土豆白菜\"到\"天南海北\"的丰富，更是通过电商全球购，我们能轻易品尝到世界各地的美食"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-1uostzo","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1uostzo","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-zrzya06","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-zrzya06","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"科技的指数级进步"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：支付方式从\"饭票\"到\"刷脸支付\"的跨越，其背后是整个中国数字基础设施的崛起"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-h3245hu","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-h3245hu","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-u4fyqr2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-u4fyqr2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"理念的根本性颠覆"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：服务的核心从\"保障生存\"转变为\"满足个性\"，体现了新时代对\"美好生活\"的更高追求"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-jfyck65","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-jfyck65","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-cqbj36i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cqbj36i","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"机遇的无限拓展"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：新时代为我们提供了前所未有的发展平台和成长机会"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ultnqwn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ultnqwn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：未来展望）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"展望未来，人工智能技术正在开启新的篇章："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-lwdhgw6","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-lwdhgw6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-qqzeig9","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qqzeig9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-zb3omua","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-zb3omua","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"智慧食堂将通过AI营养师为每个人提供个性化膳食建议"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-sigtrec","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-sigtrec","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-8u2wwys","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-8u2wwys","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"区块链技术将实现食材全程可追溯，保障食品安全"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-j6qwqzm","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-j6qwqzm","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-xhgbe07","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xhgbe07","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虚拟现实技术可能创造全新的餐饮体验场景"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-hc8el2l","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hc8el2l","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-og0a3ye","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-og0a3ye","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大数据分析将优化供应链，减少食物浪费"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-19xswnx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-19xswnx","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这些技术创新不仅改变着我们的饮食方式，更代表着新的发展机遇。作为华科学子，我们正站在这个时代的前沿，有机会参与并引领这些变革。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-si4upif","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-si4upif","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：使命担当）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"各位老师、同学，华中科技大学饮食服务的73年演变史，是中国高校发展的缩影，更是中国从站起来、富起来到强起来的生动见证。这个过程告诉我们："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-hecpn1v","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hecpn1v","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-89zhxfm","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-89zhxfm","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-1b791s0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1b791s0","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"个人命运与国家发展紧密相连"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-rwkc2tv","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-rwkc2tv","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-neu5y7e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-neu5y7e","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"科技创新是推动社会进步的重要力量"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ce3igps","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ce3igps","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-efos7iy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-efos7iy","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"新时代为我们提供了前所未有的机遇"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ja9p2x7","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ja9p2x7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-cdbwddg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cdbwddg","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们需要以更加开放的心态迎接未来"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ccsj1qe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ccsj1qe","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"作为新时代的青年，我们既是这一伟大成就的见证者和受益者，更应该是未来故事的创造者。让我们珍惜这个伟大的时代，善用科技的力量，在享受发展成果的同时，不忘奋斗初心，用我们的智慧和汗水，继续书写属于我们这一代人的精彩故事！"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vvo8rxg","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vvo8rxg","updated":"20260305082131"}},{"ID":"20260305082131-sn6fql7","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-sn6fql7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"结束页"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-uplgn6z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-uplgn6z","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"PPT提示：主标题 + 副标题 + 背景图"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vsvv4z2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vsvv4z2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（切换幻灯片：结束页）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-jibc9xi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-jibc9xi","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"主标题"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：舌尖上的华科，时代中的我们"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-b6e6ad4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-b6e6ad4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"副标题"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：拥抱新时代，共创美好未来"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ch6ezkc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ch6ezkc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"背景图"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：华科校园美景与现代化食堂的融合画面"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-74a9tu8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-74a9tu8","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"演讲时长总计"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：约24分钟"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-umh1bzc","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-umh1bzc","updated":"20260305082131"}},{"ID":"20260305082131-h3c5dyf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-h3c5dyf","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"注：本演讲稿基于历史资料和研究成果，部分细节可能存在推断，但整体脉络符合历史发展规律。"}]}]}